OL,3,COverhaul of water regulation in Wales
OL,4,Cneeded, landmark review says
OL,6,FOfwat is a non-ministerial government
OL,7,Fdepartment, which was established in
OL,8,F1989 when the water and sewerage
OL,9,Findustry in Wales and England was
OL,10,Fprivatised, while NRW is the largest
OL,11,FWelsh Government-sponsored body,
OL,12,Ffocused on tackling the climate,
OL,13,Fnature and pollution emergencies.
