OL,3,COverhaul of water regulation in Wales
OL,4,Cneeded, landmark review says
OL,6,FThe final report from the Independent
OL,7,FWater Commission, chaired by former
OL,8,FBank of England deputy governor Sir
OL,9,FJon Cunliffe, makes 88 recommendations
OL,10,Faimed at improving the sector, urging
OL,11,Fboth the Welsh and UK governments to
OL,12,Fact on growing concern over pollution,
OL,13,Fwater quality and long-term investment.
OL,15,FUK Government water minister Emma
OL,16,FHardy told broadcasters on Monday that
OL,17,Fthe system is "broken", but did not
OL,18,Fcommit to how many of the 88
OL,19,Fsuggestions would be accepted by
OL,20,FWhitehall.
