OL,3,COverhaul of water regulation in Wales
OL,4,Cneeded, landmark review says
OL,6,FThe report, published on Monday, 21
OL,7,FJuly, recommended far-reaching changes
OL,8,Fto the way the water system is
OL,9,Fregulated as it called the current
OL,10,Flandscape "fragmented and overlapping".
OL,12,FFor Wales, one of the key proposals
OL,13,Fincludes abolishing Ofwat's role, with
OL,14,Fthe regulator currently overseeing how
OL,15,Fmuch companies can charge for water
OL,16,Fand wastewater services, and
OL,17,Ftransferring those powers to NRW.
OL,26,@rD@KOUrD@fO]
