OL,6,FThe review also recommends abolishing
OL,7,Fthe Drinking Water Inspectorate, which
OL,8,Fmonitors the safety of drinking water
OL,9,Fsupplies.
OL,11,FThe Welsh Government backed the
OL,12,Fcommission's findings, saying in a
OL,13,Fstatement: "We welcome the publication
OL,14,Fof the report. This is a once in a
OL,15,Fgeneration opportunity to reset how
OL,16,FWales manages water.
