OL,6,F"Many of the recommendations will need
OL,7,Fcareful consideration and engagement
OL,8,Fto make sure we take action that is
OL,9,Fright for the people of Wales and
OL,10,Faligns with the Well-being of Future
OL,11,FGenerations Act."
OL,13,FFor England, the report advises
OL,14,Fremoving the regulatory roles of the
OL,15,FEnvironment Agency and Natural
OL,16,FEngland, which monitor the sector's
OL,17,Fimpact on nature, like companies
OL,18,Fillegally dumping sewage into
OL,19,Fwaterways.
