OL,3,COverhaul of water regulation in Wales
OL,4,Cneeded, landmark review says
OL,6,FAsked if all the recommendations would
OL,7,Fbe made law, she told the programme:
OL,8,F"What we'll do is we'll have a proper
OL,9,Flook at it all the way through the
OL,10,Fsummer and the intention is that we're
OL,11,Fgoing to introduce a White Paper to
OL,12,Fspell out exactly what we're going to
OL,13,Fdo on water reform."
OL,15,FMs Hardy said that the UK Government
OL,16,Fwould "introduce a Water Bill next
OL,17,Fyear, which will change the law", but
OL,18,Fadded: "Exactly how many out of the 88
OL,19,Fwe're going to do or not going to do,
OL,20,Fthen we'll work that out in the next
OL,21,Ffew months."
