OL,3,COverhaul of water regulation in Wales
OL,4,Cneeded, landmark review says
OL,6,FThe current system has faced intense
OL,7,Fcriticism for overseeing water
OL,8,Fcompanies during the years they paid
OL,9,Fout shareholders and accrued large
OL,10,Fdebts while ageing infrastructure
OL,11,Fcrumbled and sewage spills skyrocketed.
OL,13,FAuthor Sir Jon said the review has
OL,14,F"tried to attack the problem from all
OL,15,Fsides" but warned that bills are going
OL,16,Fto rise by 30% over the next five
OL,17,Fyears.
OL,19,F"There are some inescapable facts
OL,20,Fhere," he said.
