OL,3,COverhaul of water regulation in Wales
OL,4,Cneeded, landmark review says
OL,6,F"The cost of producing water and
OL,7,Fdealing with our wastewater is going
OL,8,Fup."
OL,10,FSir Jon later told Times Radio that
OL,11,Fregulators have failed to work
OL,12,Ftogether to make the sector deliver
OL,13,Fand blamed the Government for not
OL,14,Fgiving clear direction.
OL,16,F"It's the failure of the government to
OL,17,Fbalance out all the different
OL,18,Fpressures on water," he said, adding
OL,19,Fthat firms "need to perform better"
OL,20,Fand "be funded to invest".
