OL,6,F"Everyone knows the system is broken,"
OL,7,Fshe said. "And they give themselves
OL,8,Fhuge pay rises."
OL,10,FHowever, the minister also ruled out
OL,11,Fsupporting government intervention to
OL,12,Fcap pay in the private sector.
OL,14,FMs Hardy said: "I don't think as
OL,15,Fgovernment we should say what private
OL,16,Fcompanies should pay. But I will say `
OL,17,Fread the room. Look how angry and
OL,18,Ffurious people are."
